{
  "text": "The ARMS experiment was conducted on the European Molecular Genetics Quality Network quality certification platform. DNA was extracted from 5-to 8-\u03bcm-thick paraffin sections containing a representative portion of the tumor tissue (Qiagen DNA Mini Kit, 51304). The concentration of DNA was 20-50 ng/\u03bcL. Amplifications were performed using a 5-minute initial denaturation at 95\u00b0C, followed by [CITATION_1] ",
